Metadata.Title: Serial Killer 1: Terror in the Attic
Metadata.Description:
This is the first case of unsolved serial killer making themselves known, first in Paris.  Leaving none alive who would possibly identify them, however, on eyewitness explained a ghostly masked and hooded murderer during the gala dressed in a ancient Victorian Tuxiedo.  Perhaps it was a ghost or perhaps the serial killer wants to add a role playing element to his killing. As this case unravels we find even more questions then answers.

<HCCE>
